entities.name: Mini-Twin Instructions
entities.content:
Mini-Twin Documentation

All Pods are self-documenting. 2D data can be placed on the inside and outside of each wall. Dashboards, Charts, Lists, Signage. The data is structured so it can be read by other pods.3D data is displayed in the center of the pods.
